---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="Builder and tinkerer sharing notes on AI, tools, and side projects.">
  <main class="about-page">
    <header class="page-header content-offset">
      <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">A little context on who's writing all this.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="about-sections">
      <section class="about-row">
        <aside class="section-label">
          <span>BIO</span>
        </aside>
        <div class="section-content">
          <p>
            I'm Mohit — a developer and designer based in Bengaluru. I've been building
            things for the web for 10+ years, and these days I'm mostly obsessed with
            AI-assisted workflows, agentic development, and finding the right tool for
            every job.
          </p>
          <p>
            This site is where I share what I'm learning, tools I discover, resources I
            find useful, and updates on whatever I'm building. Think of it as my public
            notebook.
          </p>
          <p>
            By day I do freelance consulting — helping teams build AI-powered products
            and sort out their frontend and UX. The rest of the time I'm usually
            tinkering with side projects or going down some new rabbit hole.
          </p>
          <div class="section-separator" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-row">
        <aside class="section-label">
          <span>INTERESTS</span>
        </aside>
        <div class="section-content">
          <p>
            Compound engineering, AI agents, skillifying workflows into reusable systems,
            and how small teams can punch way above their weight with the right tools.
          </p>
          <div class="section-separator" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-row">
        <aside class="section-label">
          <span>CONTACT</span>
        </aside>
        <div class="section-content">
          <p>
            If something here resonated or you just want to say hi — I'm always happy to chat.
          </p>
          <ul class="contact-links">
            <li>
              <a href="https://x.com/tatermohit" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter/X</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tatermohit/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/mnttnm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding-top: clamp(0.1rem, 0.7vw, 0.42rem);
    padding-bottom: clamp(1.4rem, 2.8vw, 2.2rem);
  }

  .content-offset {
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: clamp(1.2rem, 2.4vw, 1.8rem);
  }

  .page-title {
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
    font-family: var(--entry-title-font);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    letter-spacing: 0.012em;
  }

  .about-sections {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .about-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0.72rem;
    padding-bottom: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.45rem);
  }

  .section-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .section-label span {
    font-size: 0.69rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .section-content {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .section-content p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 62ch;
  }

  .section-content p:last-of-type {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .section-separator {
    margin-top: clamp(2.2rem, 4.5vw, 3rem);
    width: 66%;
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--border-primary) 40%, transparent);
  }

  .contact-links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0 0 0;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .contact-links a {
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    padding-bottom: 0.05rem;
  }

  .contact-links a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-hover);
    border-bottom-color: var(--border-primary);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .content-offset {
      padding-left: 188px;
    }

    .about-row {
      grid-template-columns: 140px minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .section-label {
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      align-items: flex-end;
      text-align: right;
      padding-top: 0.3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
